<p>This is a list of all the topics you can subscribe to. To subscribe to a topic, just click on it!</p>
<div class="list-group">
    {{#each topics as |topic|}}
    <a href="/topics/subscribe?topic={{topic.uuid}}" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
        <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
            <h5 class="mb-1">{{topic.prettyName}}</h5>
            <small>Contains {{topic.answerableCount}} question(s)</small>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-1">{{topic.description}}</p>
        <small>{{topic.subCount}} user(s) are subscribed to this topic.</small>
    </a>
    {{/each}}
</div>
<div class="alert alert-info mt-3" role="alert">
    Note: subscriptions are only actioned once the next subscription trigger time <em>after</em> you subscribe is reached.
</div>